headline: Spellbook Raises $50M Series B to Expand AI Contract Review Platform
summary: TORONTO, October 09, 2025--Spellbook, often described as "Cursor for contracts," today announced a $50 million USD Series B funding round led by Keith Rabois, Managing Director at Khosla Ventures, with participation from Threshold Ventures, and existing investors Inovia Capital, Bling Capital, Moxxie Ventures, Path Ventures and Jean-Michel Lemieux. The capital raise values the company at $350 million post-money and brings total funding to over $80 million.
